		<a class="janrain f" href="#" data-provider="facebook" data-message="Re:How secure by MyFirstNameIsPaul" data-url="http://news.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=1715548&cid=32870798" data-title="Re:How secure">facebook</a>
		<a class="janrain l" href="#" data-provider="linkedin" data-message="Re:How secure by MyFirstNameIsPaul" data-url="http://news.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=1715548&cid=32870798" data-title="Re:How secure">linkedin</a>
