		<a class="janrain f" href="#" data-provider="facebook" data-message="It also helps solve a paradox by Sycraft-fu" data-url="http://news.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=1715548&cid=32871916" data-title="It also helps solve a paradox">facebook</a>
