		<a class="janrain f" href="#" data-provider="facebook" data-message="Still creating artificial scarcity? by lennier" data-url="http://news.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=1715548&cid=32869504" data-title="Still creating artificial scarcity?">facebook</a>
