		<a class="janrain f" href="#" data-provider="facebook" data-message="Re:Still creating artificial scarcity? by forkazoo" data-url="http://news.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=1715548&cid=32870078" data-title="Re:Still creating artificial scarcity?">facebook</a>
